message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product for $140. It's a great opportunity to get a high-quality item at a reasonable price.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $130 for the product.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Bob. I appreciate your interest in our product. I am willing to consider your offer at $135.
I understand your position, Alice. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $130 for the product. I believe this is a fair price considering its value.
Thank you for your latest counteroffer, Bob. After careful consideration, I am willing to accept $132 for the product.
